<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lei Chim Um Hi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Beita mai hen lei chimum hi,
 Lungdeih len guol kikhenna tawh;
 Natna leh lungkhamna cheng hi,
 Kumsawt kipahna la'n hungsuok hen.

[V2]
 Lungkham, buoina um ta puona,
 Hukdampa tuollenna ahi;
 Khawvel buoina thuok ta loin,
 Aw ka thagau va chawl ding na hi.

[V3]
 2. Ka lungdeihte'n zawhna pakin,
 Zion Lalpa a chawian ui;
 Keile Isu tatna zalin,
 Hehpihna gam nuomah ei puiin.

[V4]
 3. &quot;Ngaiin, hungkitpai ding kahi,
 A phat leh ni a tung zo tai;
 Tuhin thil bangkim a thaktai,
 Na Lalpa kipahna ah lutin&quot;.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>204</hymn_number>
<author>Lianvela</author>
</song>